{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Pirates of Justice (Demo)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an exciting puzzle adventure in this <strong>demo version</strong> of <strong>Pirates of Justice</strong>! Test your strategic thinking and problem-solving skills as you take on 12 engaging levels where you:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong>Drag and Drop:</strong> Place objects strategically to set the path for the bomb ball.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362380/extras/Recording_2024-11-21_035235.gif?t=1732543761\" /><br><br>2\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong>Rotate and Position:</strong> Fine-tune your setup by rotating and placing objects in the perfect spot.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362380/extras/step_2.gif?t=1732543761\" /><br><br>3\ufe0f\u20e3 <strong>Aim and Shoot:</strong> Launch the bomb ball and watch it destroy the Marine's building.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362380/extras/step_3.gif?t=1732543761\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo offers:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>12 Unique Levels</strong>: Experience a variety of obstacles and challenges to master the core mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Gameplay:</strong> Solve puzzles by carefully placing and rotating objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Taste of the Storyline:</strong> Begin your journey to fight the corrupt Marine and bring justice to the oppressed.<br><br>This product includes only the first 12 levels of the game. The full version will feature additional levels, advanced challenges, and a complete storyline.  </p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3362380?t=1732543761","background_raw":"https://s